the tree of sequences of length $< a_*$ of members of $\Delta(N_{\le c})$
possibly non-standard but of length $< a_*$.  Now apply \ref{h8}.

\noindent
3) We just repeat the proof of \ref{h8} or see \ref{c59} below.
\end{PROOF}

