\begin{claim}
\label{b20}
Assume $\bar{\bold a}$ is a $T_{{\rm ord}}-(\kappa_1,\kappa_2)$-moral
problem in $\bold m \in K^{{\rm ba}}_\kappa$ and\footnote{It seems that
